---
title: Chesapeake Cheddar Burgers with Corn on the Cob, Potato Wedges & Old Bay Aioli
description: **Now with leaner ground beef and more vegetables! You asked, we listened: This isn't the HelloFresh you remember. Bigger menu. Upgraded recipes. Increased portion sizes. More variety. The best way to cook dinner just got BETTER.**

In this extra-savory spin on burger night, spicy Old Bay seasoning and savory Worcestershire sauce add oomph to beef patties. Sizzle 'em up to perfection, add cheddar slices, then tuck them into golden toasted brioche buns spread with what we call “Old Bay-oli”—that’s mayo, mustard, garlic, and Old Bay! Serve with corn on the cob and seasoned potato wedges for a meal that satisfies.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/68765198095a7af977b01508-0f0d5c67.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/68765198095a7af977b01508-en-US.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/chesapeake-cheddar-burgers-68765198095a7af977b01508
cuisine: North America
